init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: After watching your movie, you and the others who are now sitting next to you begin to question why you all are here.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Is this place different from either of these?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The only way to move on from here is to watch your next life.
